title: #92Noon! Boudreau/Bercich/Siny/Lavelle/JG
description: Wild coach Bruce Boudreau opens the show, Pete Bercich calls in to chat VIkings, Dave Sinykin has smug takes on the Packers, Lavelle wraps up Twins season and JG steps in studio to look at Gophers/Iowa this weekend!
